L. T., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-2885 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 17, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because L. T. has failed to serve an initial brief as provided by this court's order of October 10, 2018, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

CASANUEVA, MORRIS, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
